### Scope Contract 3: Lighthouse Performance Audit — [HUMAN STEP]

**⚠ This scope is executed by the human in Chrome DevTools.**

Note: Lighthouse scores are measured with placeholder assets (small solid-color images). Scores will be artificially high. Re-run Lighthouse after real screenshots are added to get a production-representative score. The target at this stage is ≥ 90 (not ≥ 95) to account for placeholder-vs-real variance.

**Actions**
- Run Lighthouse in Chrome DevTools (Incognito mode, desktop preset) on:
  - `https://munrhalls.com`
  - `https://munrhalls.com/projects/sanglogium/`

**Human Verification Checklist**
- [ ] Homepage Lighthouse Performance ≥ 90 (placeholder assets)
- [ ] Sanglogium page Lighthouse Performance ≥ 90 (placeholder assets)
- [ ] Homepage LCP < 1.5s
- [ ] No critical Lighthouse errors (red items)
- [ ] Note: re-verify both pages after real screenshot assets are added

